item.title: Contact
item.description:
We make the first step easy. Just share a few basic details about your project and we’ll reach out to you within 24 hours to further discuss your need.

What we need from you

  • Your name & contact information
  • Project location (or area/suburb)
  • Approximate size or scope (e.g., 4-room HDB, landed house, 80 sqm condo, etc.)
  • Preferred timeline or any deadlines
  • Anything specific you already have in mind (optional)

item.title: Services
item.description:
With More than 40 Years of Hands-on Experience

At One Home Renovation, we combine over 40 years of hands-on experience: 25 years in our homeland and 15 years proudly serving the Greater Toronto Area. With expert craftsmanship to deliver exceptional results. We ogger high quality, fair pricing and on-time trustworthy service have been our commitment for decades.

Exceptional Service & Master Craftsmanship

From complex structural renovations to luxurious interior transformations, our team approaches every project with precision, care and unmatched attention to detail. We have completed countless small and large projects across the GTA, earning the trust of homeowners and businesses alike.
